<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00">啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對不起喔，<delay20 />我沒注意到你～<delay frames="40" />
因為我剛剛在想事情<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我正在考慮<delay20 />
要搬去其他島上～<delay frames="30" />
因為啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前電視裡的人說，<delay20 />
如果要成為獨立的大人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最好多去外面看看寬廣的世界喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">別走啊！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這樣啊……</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽我說，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="30" />
我<delay20 />有一件事<delay8 />
想問問看你的意見～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近在想啊，<delay20 />
感覺自己好像差不多<delay8 />
該搬去別的島了～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想外面的世界<delay20 />
一定還有很多我不知道的美食～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我打算去尋找那些美食～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我不希望你搬走！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那你要保重喔……</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來得正好～<delay frames="40" />
我剛好有事情想先跟你說～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我忘記是在哪裡讀到這段話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「如果想要成為很棒的大人，<delay8 />
就得經歷離別和相遇。」<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以說，<delay20 />
我打算要離開這裡，<delay8 />
搬到其他島去喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不可以搬走啦～！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">再見了～</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦咦？<delay20 />我不可以走嗎！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來如此，<delay8 />要是我不在的話，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />會覺得寂寞吧～<pageBreak /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我明白了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你都這麼說了，<delay20 />
那我就不搬走了～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要和你一起<delay8 />
留在<tag a="110" b="33" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />玩更多更多的遊戲喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />這麼不希望<delay20 />我搬走啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都不知道<delay8 />原來你這麼重視我，<delay20 />
我實在太開心了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />我決定了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不要搬家了～<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後我們也要<delay20 />好好相處喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />真的嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="110" b="4" />不希望我走的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我以後不會再說這種話了～<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我沒有辦法不顧你的感受<delay20 />
就這麼離開這座島呀～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後也要<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟我一起大玩特玩喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />你一直都對我很好，<delay8 />
真的很謝謝你～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算我搬去新的島，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不會忘記你的喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很謝謝你<delay20 />
常常陪我一起玩～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算住在不一樣的地方，<delay20 />
我們也一樣是好朋友喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算只花一點點時間<delay20 />
回想我和<tag a="110" b="4" />的事，<delay20 />
也能想到很多開心的回憶呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到我們以後不能再見面<delay8 />
就覺得有點寂寞，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我們還是要朝各自的目標前進喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>